This file contains the features of the program.

1. Number of Vowels

2. Number of Each Vowel

3. Case Insensitive

4. have GUI

5. Work on multiple platforms

6 Count the number of words

7 Frequency of each word

7 Count number of phrases

9 Count number of paragraphs

10 Read text from a file , text or URL

11 Number of consonant

12 Number of Each consonant

13 (experimental) Text title suggestion based on the most frequen words

14 Text encryption/decryption

15 Compare provide words/phase and count number of occurrances

16 Filter words to uniquely count words greater or lesser than a number

17 Same as 16 but for sentences

18 Export to other file formats such as pdf, word, excel

19 Skin/Theme

20 Find and Replace tool
